title: FA Cup fifth round scores LIVE: Huddersfield vs Man City | Daily Mail Online
text: FA Cup fifth round scores LIVE: Huddersfield v Manchester City, Middlesbrough v Oxford United and Millwall v Leicester City FA Cup fifth round continues in earnest on Saturday afternoon with three ties Huddersfield entertain Manchester City in the pick of the matches on offer Manchester City captain Vincent Kompany is ruled out injured League One side Oxford make trip to the North East to take on Middlesbrough Millwall host Leicester City with all three matches due to kick off at 3pm GMT
